test_all_one_range:
assert [1, 3, 5] == [1, 1, 1, 1]
  At index 1 diff: 3 != 1
  Right contains one more item: 1
  Full diff:
  - [1, 1, 1, 1]
  + [1, 3, 5]
test_odd_same_number:
assert [1, 3, 5] == [-11, -11, -11, -11]
  At index 0 diff: 1 != -11
  Right contains one more item: -11
  Full diff:
  - [-11, -11, -11, -11]
  + [1, 3, 5]
test_even_range:
assert [1, 3, 5] == []
  Left contains 3 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [1, 3, 5]
